data.description:
Discover the potential of this fixer-upper gem situated in the heart of desirable Ormond Beach! This remarkable opportunity presents an affordable chance to acquire a home well below its market value, allowing you to unlock significant value through your creative vision and renovation efforts.Nestled on a tranquil side street, this house offers a serene setting while remaining conveniently connected to the vibrant offerings of the area. Immerse yourself in the beauty of Central Park, explore nearby bike paths, and perhaps indulge in a round of golf at the prestigious Riviera Country Club.With a projected after-renovation value of $320,000, this property holds the promise of an exceptional return on investment once transformed. Whether you're an investor seeking to capitalize on a lucrative venture or a homeowner looking to craft your dream abode, the potential here is undeniable.

We welcome a variety of financing options to accommodate your preferences:
(1) Cash: Streamline the purchase process and embark on your renovation journey swiftly.
(2) Hard Money Loan: Access the funds needed to revive this property to its full potential.
(3) 203(k) FHA Loan: Leverage this loan option to combine purchase and renovation costs into one convenient package.


The square footage of the Property has not been measured by Seller, Seller's agents, or Broker (including square footage of the lot and home), and the square footage and other information quoted on any marketing tools such as advertisements, brochures, MLS data, websites and any other information provided based on information supplied by Seller or Broker is deemed approximate and not guaranteed. Buyer further acknowledges that Buyer shall not rely upon any such square footage and other information quoted on any marketing tools are not representations and/or warranties of Seller, Seller's agents, or Broker.
